{{Quote|I am ashamed, my brother. In happier times&mdash;before our two races signed the Concordat of Peace&mdash;a warrior of the 12 Tribes would die rather than flee from you nightskins.|Kéral Longknife|<ref name="marvel53">[[Star Wars (1977) 53|''Star Wars'' (1977) 53]]</ref>}}
[[File:Tsyriel1.jpg|thumb|right|100px|Kéral Longknife, Demarch of the Twelve Tribes of T'Syriél.]]
The '''Twelve Tribes of T'Syriél''' was the tribal coalition of the native [[T'Syriél]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Shiva IV]] during the era of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Inheritors of a proud warrior tradition, the tribes warred for generations with the [[Human/Legends|human]] [[Calian Confederacy]], until [[Demarch]] [[Kéral Longknife]] signed the [[Concordat of Peace]] with Calian [[Warlord/Legends|Warlord]] [[Aron Peacebringer]] in [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]] and pledged to unify with each other. The tribes' martial strength waned in the months after the cessation of hostilities, and Longknife lamented his people's loss of fighting spirit. Some T'Syriél were outcast from tribal society afterward, retreating to lives of banditry in the wastes.<ref name="marvel53" />

